@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8080

### Stage 31：重建真实 Qdrant 索引
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/advanced/vectors/rebuild

### Stage 32：混合检索与重排
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/advanced/search
Content-Type: application/json

{"query":"人工智能 知识管理","mode":"HYBRID","rerank":true,"recall":10,"limit":5,"reliabilityWeight":0.2,"freshnessWeight":0.2}

### Stage 33：Crossref 学术搜索
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/advanced/academic/search
Content-Type: application/json

{"query":"knowledge management","doi":"","author":"","fromDate":"2024-01-01"}

### Stage 36：刷新监控指标
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/advanced/monitor

### Stage 37：ntfy 测试通知
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/advanced/notifications/test
Content-Type: application/json

{"url":"http://ntfy:80","topic":"knowledge-alerts","title":"Knowledge Collector 测试","message":"Stage 37 通知链路验证通过"}

### Stage 38：n8n Webhook（先在 n8n 导入并激活 deploy/n8n/knowledge-collector-workflow.json）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/advanced/workflows/trigger
Content-Type: application/json

{"webhook":"http://n8n:5678/webhook/knowledge-collector","contentType":"ARTICLE","businessId":1,"summary":"Stage 38 可验证示例"}

### Stage 35：查看 AI 调用记录
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/advanced/executions?stage=34&limit=50

### 全阶段执行历史
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/advanced/executions?limit=100
